    "MissionGiver": "Ling Family Hauling",
    "Title": "Ling Family Seeking New Contractors",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nWe're a small family owned and operated delivery company that's currently seeking new contractors in the Crusader area. \n\nIf you're interested in working with us, the following delivery would be a great trial to see if you're a good match for the company.\n\nPACKAGE FOR PICK UP\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> from <EM4>~mission(Pickup1|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Dropoff1|Address)</EM4>\n\nIf all goes well, you'll become the newest member of Ling Family Hauling.\n\nLast thing, it'd probably be a good idea to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with. \n\nThanks, \nConni Ling\nShipment Coordinator\nLing Family Hauling",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi,\n\nWe're a small family owned and operated delivery company that's currently seeking new contractors in the Crusader area. \n\nIf you're interested in working with us, the following delivery would be a great trial to see if you're a good match for the company.\n\nPACKAGE FOR PICK UP\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#[Item1|SerialNumber]</EM4> from <EM4>[Pickup1|Address]</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#[Item1|SerialNumber]</EM4> to <EM4>[Dropoff1|Address]</EM4>\n\nIf all goes well, you'll become the newest member of Ling Family Hauling.\n\nLast thing, it'd probably be a good idea to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with. \n\nThanks, \nConni Ling\nShipment Coordinator\nLing Family Hauling",
